# See either of these for more info:
# https://alexpearce.me/2014/05/italics-in-iterm2-vim-tmux/
# http://muddygoat.org/articles/italic-terminal-tmux
# http://www.nerdyweekly.com/posts/enable-italic-text-vim-tmux-gnome-terminal/
#
# Apply by using:
# - sudo tic ~/.dotfiles/term/screen-256color-italic.terminfo
screen-256color-italic|screen with 256 colors and italic,
  sitm=\E[3m, ritm=\E[23m,
  use=screen-256color,

